    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8 min, or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>While the pasta cooks, drain the <strong>tomato[es]</strong>, then refill the bowl with <strong>ice-cold water </strong>and set them aside to cool</p><p>Once the pasta is cooked, drain and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy</strong> <strong>pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/767-Step-2-x200.jpg",
