    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives </strong>finely</p><p>Zest half your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>(try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter!)</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> [100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
