    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain then peel the skin off the <strong>tomato[es]</strong>, starting from the<strong> </strong>cross</p><p>Chop the <strong>tomato[es] </strong>into quarters, scoop out and discard the seeds so that you end up with tomato petals</p><p>Carefully and using a sharp knife, dice the <strong>tomato petals </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato concasse</strong></p>",
