    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>to large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>lemon zest </strong>and cook for 1 min until golden and aromatic</p>",
      "order": 5,
