    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and cook for 1 min or until it’s evaporated</p><p>Once evaporated, add the <strong>vegetable stock </strong>and cook for a further 2 min or until it’s reduced down to a sauce</p>",
