    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the pan from the heat and stir in your <strong>crab meat</strong>, <strong>clotted cream</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard, half </strong>of the<strong> tomato concasse</strong> and<strong> half</strong> of the <strong>chopped chives </strong>(save the rest for later!)</p><p>Add the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>linguine</strong> and the juice of your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy crab linguine</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
